      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how much pain you are in, and I understand why you feel my suggestions feel like an insult to your grief. Please know that your feelings are valid even when they seem impossible to change, and there are people who can sit with you in the dark if you choose to reach out. You do not have to carry this burden alone today, and there is always someone who would want to help you find a way through this heaviness.",
